  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This is a game that simulates the survival, development and exploration of civilization in the game. The game is divided into three parts.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>1. Sky of Chaos. </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Civilization exists, develops, and evolves in a world of three or more bodies, with the ultimate goal of escaping from chaotic star systems.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2. Suspicion of Abyss.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Civilization is in a star cluster, facing a major test of the Dark Forest Law. The difficult decision is whether to hide or attack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3. Galaxy of Slaughter.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Numerous civilizations are fighting, expanding, and upgrading within a galaxy, and only one civilization can achieve ultimate victory.</p>",
